[[File:Steven Grant in Cupcake Van.png|{{AltFloat}}|Grant holding a gun to his shock]]
This forced Spector or Lockley to take control over the body again, with Spector or Lockley managing to defeat his enemies once again to drive back to safety. However, before he could do so, he was once again taken back over by Grant, who irresponsibly threw his own weapon at his enemies in a panic, much to the voice's dismay.
