{{Quote|Where are we going?"<br>"Where the hell do you think?|Marc Spector and [[Khonshu]]|Summon the Suit}}
Spector was brought to [[Cairo]], [[Egypt]] by [[Khonshu]] so that they could find the [[Tomb of Alexander the Great|tomb]] of [[Ammit]] before Harrow could. He sat shirtless on the floor next to his bed and finished off a bottle of alcohol, bloody knuckles and broken mirrors insinuating that Spector had another fight with Grant.
