{{Quote|You killed him? I needed to talk to that guy. About a dig site. Guess I'm gonna have to talk to you instead.|Marc Spector to [[Alpha (Disciples of Ammit)|Alpha]]|The Friendly Type}}
Spector then went exploring [[Cairo]] and found [[Disciples of Ammit]] spying on him. He ran after them over rooftops until he caught up to them. He facetiously asked them what they were doing, whether fighting or dancing, as one of them made a excessive movement with his feet on the ground.
